p.k: During the gang's Halloween party, Unikitty discovers Brick isn't scared of anything! / The gang’s board game night gets too competitive. / Unikitty keeps losing at videogames, so gets a super-powered controller from Dr. Fox. Surprisingly, it controls people & the castle goes into lockdown like a real-world videogame! / When Puppycorn uses a wishing well & it doesn’t come true, Unikitty is shocked to discover that all the wishes can’t be granted because they’re trapped at the bottom of the well!
